'''''All Sons & Daughters''''' is the eponymously titled second studio album from the American Christian worship duo [[All Sons & Daughters]]. The album was released on May 6, 2014 by [[Integrity Media|Integrity Music]] and [[Columbia Records]]. It was produced by Paul Brendon Mabury and Shane D. Wilson. The album charted on the ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' [[Billboard 200|200]] at No. 58, and it received a five star rating from ''[[Worship Leader (magazine)|Worship Leader]]'', four-and-a-half star ratings from Jesus Freak Hideout and New Release Tuesday and a four star rating from Indie Vision Music.

==Background==
The eponymously titled second studio album from All Sons & Daughters releases on May 6, 2014 by [[Integrity Media|Integrity Music]] and [[Columbia Records]] that was produced by Paul Brendon Mabury and Shane D. Wilson.

